Beginner Neural Network - In Progress Project

Motivation
  This project contains a neural network class to help determine if a series of 
  0 or 1 inputs match an AND, OR, or XOR logic pattern. 
  
Status
  Project is currently complete, with one unresolved bug due to time constraints. 

Additional Details
  "network.h" has been supplied by the instructor; my edits have been commented on. All other code
  written by me. 
